rows.label: tlk42100141_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Us Phonex couldn't possibly imagine
moving to another Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk42100141_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I've always lived here, by
this tree, and that's the
way it's going to stay.

rows.label: tlk42100141_02_msg0003
rows.name:
If there were a Phonex brave enough
to go on such an adventure... Why,
they'd be no less than a hero.
